{
  "stem": "24259.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was quite small, and it was a man's bike with the bar and I actually couldn't reach over the bar, so I learned how to ride underneath the bar.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's how I learned how to ride a bike.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Teachers were primarily rabbis and most of the teaching was, you know, Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember some math.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember one rabbi specifically.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had a long, black beard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and occasionally he'd come to the house and complain about my misbehavior.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my father would give him something as a tip for doing it, so he used to like doing that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would get a beating.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'd get disciplined.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not that I recall.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just remembered having to say the morning prayers, and the afternoon prayers, and evening prayers every day.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember math.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I guess I was a fairly good student as well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were quite a few.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'd say uncertainty in the thousands.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And occasionally, they would have like demonstrations, being pro-Israel or pro-Palestine at the time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And again, they would have different organizations, one of which was called the Betar.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And kind of, we would dress up almost like Boy Scouts here in the United States.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's the best way to describe the way we would look.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was primarily a Zionist type of an organization, pro-Israel and so forth.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they would be educating us and being for Israel or Palestine at the time, again.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Adults as well were organized and-- at times.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We have-- I have pictures of my father, everybody being lined up in a marching position, if you will, holding various signs and so forth.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I guess we would call them a demonstration for Israel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Definitely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember a lot of children.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
